   "source": [
    "## 3. Deep Dive: Focus Genres\n",
    "\n",
    "Based on the full landscape scan, we now zoom into our four focus genres: **Pop, R&B, Rock, and Jazz**.\n",
    "\n",
    "> **Reusability:** To analyse different genres, simply change the `FOCUS_GENRES` variable in Cell 2 and re-run all cells."
   ]
  },
  {
